🔹 Input + If-Else Based Questions
Take a number from a textbox and check if it is even or odd.
Take age input and check if the person is eligible to vote (18+).
Take a number and check if it is positive, negative, or zero.
Take marks input and display Pass or Fail (>= 40 pass).
Take two numbers and find the greater number using if-else.
🔹 For Loop Based Questions
Take a number and print numbers from 1 to N.
Print even numbers from 1 to 50 using for loop.
Take a number and print its multiplication table.
Find the sum of numbers from 1 to N.
Reverse a number using a for loop (e.g., 123 → 321).
🔹 While Loop Based Questions
Print numbers from 1 to 10 using while loop.
Take a number and print its digits one by one using while loop.
Find the sum of digits of a number using while loop.
Check whether a number is palindrome using while loop.
Count number of digits in a number using while loop.
🔹 Array Based Questions
Take 5 numbers in an array and find the largest number.
Find the sum of all elements in an array.
Count how many even numbers are in an array.
Reverse an array without using built-in functions.
Search for a number in an array and print found / not found.
